commit.message:
gcse.c (update_ld_motion_stores): Don't use variable I for an insn.

	* gcse.c (update_ld_motion_stores): Don't use variable I for an insn.
	* flow.c (set_block_for_new_insns): Remove needless cast and
	properly check for unset block number.

From-SVN: r41227
